How Many Ways We Can Execute FrameWork/Test Cases
-----------------------------------------------------

1)TestNG.xml
2)pom.xml
3)command prompt
4)run.bat
5)Jenkins.

pom.xml
----------
2 plugins are Required to execute project through pom.xml file

1)maven-complier-plugin
2)maven-surefire-plugin
Execute test cases though command prompt:-
----------------------------------------------
maven
-------
    -->available as a plugin within eclipse.
    -->available as maven software on Os.
    
How to install Maven on window os:
-------------------------------------

1)download maven & Extract zip file
http://mirrors.estointernet.in/apache/maven/maven-3/3.6.1/binaries/apache-maven-3.6.1-bin.zip

2)set maven installed on window or not

3)Verify maven installed on window or not

    cd C:\Users\gowth\eclipse-workspace\selenium ecllipse\RestAssuredApiTesting_Employee_Project
    mvn clean install

Execute test cases using run.bat file
---------------------------------------
Create run.bat file


Execute test cases using jenkins:-
-----------------------------------------
1)Download jenkins: http:/mirrors.jenkins.io/war-stable/latest/jenkins.war

open command prompt , go to file location;

java -jar jenkins.war


Phases
