Git & GitHub:
---------------------

step1: Sign up to GitHub repository & get the account
step2: Login to gitHub
step3: Create a new repository
        http://github.com/growth/RstAssuredApiTesting.git
        
step4: Cloning Local git repository within eclipse using GithubURL

step5: Add our project to Local git repository

      RightClick-->Share Project-->Select local repository from dropdown -->Finish
      
      RightClick-->Add to Index
      
      RightClick-->team-->Commit
      
      Version control System 

